title: Patriots Honor 3rd Annual Golf Tournament
text:
Patriots Honor 3rd Annual Golf Tournament Where Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, Sports 3rd Annual Golf Tournament benefitting programs for Injured Veterans. Nov. 6, 2015 Lincoln Hills Golf Course 7:30am check in 9am Shotgun start. $80 and $90 after October 24, 2015.
